title: Minister of Finance chairs a meeting on Post-SOM Reforms and Road to Brussels with Ambassadors ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Finance - Islamic Republic of Afghanistan ) 7th October 2015 : H.E. Eklil Hakimi, the Minister of finance met with 5+ 3+3 Ambassadors on Wednesday, 7th October in Presidential Palace , Char Chinar to discuss Post- SOM
